name: Dungeness Wallpaper - Chalkhill Blue
description:
The first design from Mini Moderns 'Hinterland' collection. Mini Moderns take a stroll along the shingle and explore the magical landscape of Dungeness. Our latest wallpaper features a mass of shingle, punctuated by illustrated vignettes of quaint cabins, abandoned fishing boats and ramshackle huts. Anchoring the print are the two lighthouses that flank the Mini Moderns beach house. 

Available soon in 5 colourways.

52cm x 10m ROLL
PRINTED IN THE UK WITH WATERBASED INKS ON PAPER FROM SUSTAINED FORESTS
52cm REPEAT - HALF DROP

name: Sound of the Suburbs Bone China Mug
description:
Our 'Buddha of Suburbia' journey from glam to punk concludes with this limited edition Sound of the Suburbs mug.

It commemorates the Today show appearance of the Sex Pistols and their entourage. Broadcast live to a London-only audience, the controversial interview ended presenter Bill Grundy's career and next day made the front page of the tabloids. For Northern boys like us, and probably many denizens of the suburbs, it was the first we'd heard of punk, and the start of something new.

BONE CHINA WITH PLATINUM PRINT

HAND DECORATED IN THE UK BY NICE PEOPLE

name: Mini Moderns Environmentally Responsible Paint - CONCRETE™
description:
Our Festival print was conceived in homage to the 1951 Festival of Britain, so what could be more fitting than a modernist concrete grey as the hero colourway?

Our specialist paint manufacturers have reprocessed waste water-based paint to create a premium grade matt emulsion with lovely coverage and a chalky finish.

RECLAIMED, RESPONSIBLE, RESPLENDENT.

All products in our paint range contain up to 90% recycled content, made up from waste paint that has been diverted from landfill or incineration. No, we couldn't believe it was possible either!

MADE IN THE UK BY NICE PEOPLE.

For a limited period, our colour card is available free of charge. Please email us with your address to receive one - info@minimoderns.com

Our paint currently ships only within the UK.
